Service Catalog Action Reference (Beta)

Review the actions associated with Service Catalog.
Available in: Lightning Experience, Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited Editions with Einstein for Service and Customer Service Catalog add-on licenses.

Service Catalog provides these actions to resolve common contact reasons using Copilot:
Update Phone Number
Update Email Address
Open a Support Case

These actions are custom-built for Service Catalog and each is associated with an item of the same name. You must have the associated licensing for Service Catalog and Einstein licensing to access Service Catalog actions.

Copilot Action: Update Email Address (Beta)
Creates a Service Catalog request for the Update Email Address catalog item.
Available in: Lightning Experience, Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited Editions with Einstein for Service and Customer Service Catalog add-on licenses.
API Name	UpdateEmailAddress
Action Type	Custom
Reference Action Type	Service Catalog Item
Inputs	previousEmailAddress, newEmailAddress
Outputs	svcItemRequestId

Copilot Action: Update Phone Number (Beta)
Creates a Service Catalog request for the Update Phone Number catalog item.
Available in: Lightning Experience, Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited Editions with Einstein for Service and Customer Service Catalog add-on licenses.
API Name	UpdatePhoneNumber
Action Type	Custom
Reference Action Type	Service Catalog Item
Inputs	Email, NewPhoneNumber
Outputs	svcItemRequestId

Copilot Action: Get Help (Beta)
Creates a Service Catalog request for the Get Help catalog item.
Available in: Lightning Experience, Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited Editions with Einstein for Service and Customer Service Catalog add-on licenses.
API Name	GetHelp
Action Type	Custom
Reference Action Type	Service Catalog Item
Inputs	Email_Input, Description_Input
Outputs	svcItemRequestId
